textbox_5.text: I did not have a strategy really I just based my answer on what looked similar. I thought about basing it on if you mix two colours what do you get, and is it similar but thought that would just confuse me so I kept it simple.
textbox_7.text: When I first started it seemed easy but as I continued I started doubting my ability to know colour and I am a woman so it should be easy. So it was really an interesting and challenging survey to just trust in one's judgment and not try to complicate things.
